---
title: Spiced Chicken & Bacon Caesar-Style Salad with Garlic Roast Potatoes & Cherry BBQ Sauce
description: Let’s get this dinner started with crispy chicken bites and a cherry BBQ sauce to glaze the chicken so your mouth really starts
watering. Toss it through the caesar salad with bacon and croutons, a must have in any caesar salad.
